<title>USA: ATS Medical device implanted for first time.</title>
<headline>ATS Medical device implanted for first time.</headline>
<dateline>MINNEAPOLIS 1997-01-07</dateline>
<text>
<p>ATS Medical Inc said Tuesday its Open Pivot heart valve was implanted for the first time in the United States at a Minneapolis hospital.</p>
<p>The company said a cardiac surgeon implanted the device into a 70-year-old woman at Abbott Northwestern Hospital.</p>
<p>ATS Medical said it is now prepared to begin clinical studies on the valve in the United States, which represents almost half of the worldwide market for the device.</p>
<p>The company makes pyrolytic carbon open pivot mechanical heart valves. Its stock was up 1/8 Tuesday at 7-7/8.</p>
<p>((Chicago newsdesk (312) 408-8787))</p>
